msgstr "ସହାୟିକା ସିଷ୍ଟମ"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:121
msgid ""
"Sahayika is a digital platform developed to simplify the management of Self "
"Help Groups (SHGs). It replaces traditional manual record-keeping methods "
"with a structured and efficient system where all financial and member-"
"related data can be stored, accessed, and managed in one place."
msgstr ""
"ସହାୟିକା ହେଉଛି ଏକ ଡିଜିଟାଲ ପ୍ଲାଟଫର୍ମ ଯାହା ସ୍ୱୟଂ ସହାୟକ ଗୋଷ୍ଠୀ (SHG) ପରିଚାଳନାକୁ ସହଜ କରିବା "
"ପାଇଁ ଉନ୍ନତ କରାଯାଇଛି। ଏହା ପାରମ୍ପରିକ ହସ୍ତଲିଖିତ ରେକର୍ଡ ପ୍ରଣାଳୀକୁ ପରିବର୍ତ୍ତନ କରି ଏକ ସଂଗଠିତ ଏବଂ "
"କାର୍ଯ୍ୟକ୍ଷମ ପ୍ରଣାଳୀ ପ୍ରଦାନ କରେ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:126
msgid ""
"The main purpose of this system is to improve transparency, reduce errors, "
"and save time in handling group activities such as savings collection, loan "
"distribution, and repayment tracking. It ensures that every transaction is "
"properly recorded and easily accessible when needed."
msgstr ""
"ଏହି ପ୍ରଣାଳୀର ପ୍ରଧାନ ଉଦ୍ଦେଶ୍ୟ ହେଉଛି ପ୍ରକାଶ୍ୟତା ବଢ଼ାଇବା, ତ୍ରୁଟି କମେଇବା ଏବଂ ସଂଚୟ, ଋଣ ବଣ୍ଟନ ଓ "
"ଫେରତ ଟ୍ରାକିଂ ପରି କାର୍ଯ୍ୟଗୁଡ଼ିକୁ ସହଜ କରିବା।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:130
msgid "How to Use the System"
msgstr "ସିଷ୍ଟମ୍ କିପରି ବ୍ୟବହାର କରିବେ"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:133
msgid ""
"Users can log in to the system using their credentials. Based on their role, "
"such as President or Member, they can perform different actions. The "
"President can add members, record monthly collections, and manage loans, "
"while members can view their savings, loan details, and payment status."
msgstr ""
"ବ୍ୟବହାରକାରୀମାନେ ନିଜ ଲଗଇନ ସୂଚନା ଦ୍ୱାରା ସିଷ୍ଟମ୍‌କୁ ପ୍ରବେଶ କରିପାରିବେ। ପଦବୀ ଅନୁଯାୟୀ ସେମାନେ "
"ଭିନ୍ନ କାମ କରିପାରିବେ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:137
msgid ""
"To view past records, users can select a specific month and year in the "
"monthly collection and loan tracking sections. This allows easy access to "
"historical data without confusion."
msgstr "ପୁରୁଣା ରେକର୍ଡ ଦେଖିବା ପାଇଁ ବ୍ୟବହାରକାରୀମାନେ ମାସ ଓ ବର୍ଷ ବାଛିପାରିବେ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:141
msgid "Rules and Guidelines"
msgstr "ନିୟମ ଓ ନିର୍ଦ୍ଦେଶନାମା"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:144
msgid ""
"All entries must be recorded accurately at the time of the meeting to "
"maintain correct financial data. Only authorized users should be allowed to "
"add or modify records. Members should regularly check their data to ensure "
"transparency and correctness."
msgstr ""
"ସମସ୍ତ ତଥ୍ୟ ସଠିକ ଭାବେ ରେକର୍ଡ କରିବା ଆବଶ୍ୟକ। କେବଳ ଅଧିକୃତ ବ୍ୟକ୍ତିମାନେ ତଥ୍ୟ ପରିବର୍ତ୍ତନ କରିପାରିବେ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:148
msgid ""
"Loan repayments and savings contributions should be updated monthly. Any "
"delay or incorrect entry may affect the overall group financial report. "
"Proper usage of the system ensures fairness and accountability among all "
"members."
msgstr "ଋଣ ଫେରତ ଓ ସଂଚୟ ପ୍ରତିମାସ ଅଦ୍ୟତନ କରିବା ଆବଶ୍ୟକ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:152
msgid "Benefits of Digital System"
msgstr "ଡିଜିଟାଲ ସିଷ୍ଟମର ଲାଭ"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:155
msgid ""
"Using a digital system like Sahayika reduces dependency on paper records, "
"minimizing the risk of data loss or damage. It also provides faster access "
"to information, making decision-making easier for the group."
msgstr "ଡିଜିଟାଲ ସିଷ୍ଟମ ବ୍ୟବହାର କରିଲେ କାଗଜ ଉପରେ ନିର୍ଭରଶୀଳତା କମେ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:159
msgid ""
"The system improves accuracy in calculations, automatically tracks totals, "
"and helps monitor loan repayments efficiently. It also enhances "
"transparency, as every member can view their own financial status clearly."
msgstr "ଏହି ସିଷ୍ଟମ ଗଣନାର ସଠିକତା ବଢ଼ାଏ ଓ ସମସ୍ତ ତଥ୍ୟ ସହଜରେ ଦେଖାଯାଏ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:163
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "ନିଷ୍କର୍ଷ"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:166
msgid ""
"Sahayika is a reliable and user-friendly solution for managing SHG "
"activities digitally. By adopting this system, groups can ensure better "
"organization, improved financial control, and long-term sustainability."
msgstr "ସହାୟିକା ହେଉଛି SHG ପରିଚାଳନା ପାଇଁ ଏକ ବିଶ୍ୱସନୀୟ ଓ ସହଜ ସମାଧାନ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:174 .\templates\index.html:151
msgid "Member Management"
msgstr "ସଦସ୍ୟ ପରିଚାଳନା"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:175
msgid "Easily add and manage all SHG members in one place."
msgstr "ସମସ୍ତ ସଦସ୍ୟଙ୍କୁ ସହଜରେ ପରିଚାଳନା କରନ୍ତୁ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:183
msgid "Track loan distribution, EMI payments, and balances."
msgstr "ଋଣ ଓ EMI ଟ୍ରାକ କରନ୍ତୁ।"

#: .\main\templates\learn_more.html:190
msgid "Reports & Insights"
